1. *Zabavna* igračka je privukla pažnju dece. (Fun toy attracted the attention of children.)
2. On je *zabavan* sagovornik. (He is a fun conversationalist.)
3. Ovaj film je veoma *zabavan*. (This movie is very entertaining.)
4. Njihov odnos je postao manje *zabavan*. (Their relationship has become less fun.)
5. *Zabavni* park je mesto koje deca obožavaju. (An amusement park is a place that children love.)
6. On voli da bude *zabavan* na društvenim okupljanjima. (He likes to be fun at social gatherings.)
7. Njihov poslednji zajednički izlet bio je vrlo *zabavan*. (Their last trip together was very enjoyable.)
8. Ova knjiga ima *zabavan* stil pisanja. (This book has an entertaining writing style.)
9. *Zabavni* program privukao je veliki broj ljudi. (The entertainment program attracted a large number of people.)
10. Ona je *zabavna* osoba koju ljudi vole da okruže. (She is a fun person that people like to be around.)